<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9846</anchor> <rss>erct-002D.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Lemma</taxon> <addr>erct-002D</addr>  <route>erct-002D.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>30</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>From <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinverses</link> to <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverses</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002D.agda" type="external">erct-002D.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Let <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> be <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link> with <tex>s,r \colon  B \to  A</tex> and <tex>h_s \colon  f  \circ  s  \sim   1_{ B }</tex> and <tex>h_r \colon  r \circ  f =  1_{ A }</tex>. Then we may define a homotopy <tex>h'  \colon  s \circ  f  \sim   1_{ A }</tex> exhibiting <tex>s \colon  B \to  A</tex> as a retraction of <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex>. Therefore, we may define a <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverse</link> to <tex>f</tex> tracked by <tex>s \colon  B \to  A</tex>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9847</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>30</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>   </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>We have <tex>s \circ  f  \sim  r \circ  f  \circ  s \circ  f</tex> by <tex>h_r</tex> and <tex>r \circ  f  \circ  s \circ  f \sim  r  \circ  f</tex> by <tex>h_s</tex> and <tex>r \circ  f  \sim   1_{ A }</tex> by <tex>h_r</tex>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> <backmatter><contributions/> <context><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9848</anchor> <rss>erct-003M.rss.xml</rss>  <addr>erct-003M</addr>  <route>erct-003M.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>19</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title><link href="erct-000Z.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Z" title="Functions and inverses">Functions and inverses</link> › conversion lemmas</title> <parent>erct-000Z</parent> </frontmatter> <mainmatter><tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="true" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9849</anchor> <rss>erct-003C.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Lemma</taxon> <addr>erct-003C</addr>  <route>erct-003C.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>1</month> <day>3</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>From <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverses</link> to <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinverses</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-003C.agda" type="external">erct-003C.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Any <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-invertible</link> map <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> is <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">biinvertible</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9850</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2024</year> <month>1</month> <day>3</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>   </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>The <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverse</link> to <tex>f</tex> is simultaneously a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">section</link> and a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">retraction</link>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="true" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9851</anchor> <rss>erct-002C.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Lemma</taxon> <addr>erct-002C</addr>  <route>erct-002C.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>30</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>From <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverses</link> to coherent <link href="erct-000W.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000W" title="Inverse">inverses</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002C.agda" type="external">erct-002C.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Let <tex>f  \colon  A  \to  B</tex> have a <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverse</link> <tex>g \colon  B \to  A</tex> with incoherent counit <tex>\epsilon \colon  f \circ  g \sim   1_{ B }</tex> and unit <tex>\eta \colon  g \circ  f \sim   1_{ A }</tex>. We can <em>correct</em> the counit to obtain a coherent <link href="erct-000W.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000W" title="Inverse">inverse</link> to <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9852</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>30</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>   </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>The corrected counit <tex>\epsilon '  \colon  g \circ  f \sim   1_{ A }</tex> is defined like so:</p>
 <tex display="block">
   \epsilon ' x : \equiv 
   \epsilon \mathopen {} \left ( f \mathopen {} \left ( f ^{-1}  x \right ) \mathclose {} \right ) \mathclose {} ^{-1}   \cdot   \mathsf {act}_{ f } \mathopen {} \left ( \eta \mathopen {} \left ( f ^{-1}  x \right ) \mathclose {} \right ) \mathclose {}   \cdot   \epsilon  x
 </tex>

 <p>The coherence <tex>\chi \colon   \mathsf {act}_{ f } \circ   \eta   \sim   \epsilon ' \circ  f</tex> can be constructed using our two naturality lemmas <ref addr="erct-001V" href="erct-001V.xml" taxon="Lemma"/> and <ref addr="erct-001W" href="erct-001W.xml" taxon="Lemma"/>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="true" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9853</anchor> <rss>erct-002D.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Lemma</taxon> <addr>erct-002D</addr>  <route>erct-002D.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>30</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>From <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinverses</link> to <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverses</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002D.agda" type="external">erct-002D.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Let <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> be <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link> with <tex>s,r \colon  B \to  A</tex> and <tex>h_s \colon  f  \circ  s  \sim   1_{ B }</tex> and <tex>h_r \colon  r \circ  f =  1_{ A }</tex>. Then we may define a homotopy <tex>h'  \colon  s \circ  f  \sim   1_{ A }</tex> exhibiting <tex>s \colon  B \to  A</tex> as a retraction of <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex>. Therefore, we may define a <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">quasi-inverse</link> to <tex>f</tex> tracked by <tex>s \colon  B \to  A</tex>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9854</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>30</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>   </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>We have <tex>s \circ  f  \sim  r \circ  f  \circ  s \circ  f</tex> by <tex>h_r</tex> and <tex>r \circ  f  \circ  s \circ  f \sim  r  \circ  f</tex> by <tex>h_s</tex> and <tex>r \circ  f  \sim   1_{ A }</tex> by <tex>h_r</tex>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree></mainmatter> </tree></context> <related><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9855</anchor> <rss>erct-000U.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-000U</addr>  <route>erct-000U.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>19</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Biinverse</title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000U.agda" type="external">erct-000U.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>A <em><strong>biinverse</strong></em> to a function <tex>f \colon  A  \to  B</tex> is defined to be a pair of a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">section</link> and a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">retraction</link> to <tex>f</tex>. We will refer to a function <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> equipped with a biinverse as a <em><strong>biinvertible function</strong></em>.</p></mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9856</anchor> <rss>erct-000X.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-000X</addr>  <route>erct-000X.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>19</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Quasi-inverse</title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000X.agda" type="external">erct-000X.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>A <em><strong>quasi-inverse</strong></em> to a function <tex>f  \colon  A  \to  B</tex> is a function <tex>g  \colon  B  \to  A</tex> equipped with homotopies <tex>\epsilon \colon  f  \circ  g  \sim   1_{ B }</tex> and <tex>\eta \colon  g  \circ  f  \sim 1_{ A }</tex>, rendering <tex>g</tex> simultaneously a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">section</link> and a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">retraction</link> of <tex>f</tex>.</p><p>Although no coherence laws are assumed for <tex>\eta</tex> and <tex>\epsilon</tex>, we shall refer to them respectively as the <em>unit</em> and <em>counit</em> of the quasi-inverse.</p></mainmatter> </tree></related> <backlinks><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9857</anchor> <rss>erct-002N.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Corollary</taxon> <addr>erct-002N</addr>  <route>erct-002N.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title><link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">Biinvertible</link> maps are <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map">contractible</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002N.agda" type="external">erct-002N.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Any <link href="erct-000X.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000X" title="Quasi-inverse">biinvertible</link> map <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> is <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map">contractible</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>9858</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>  <parent>erct-002N</parent> </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>As <link href="erct-002D.xml" type="local" addr="erct-002D" title="From biinverses to quasi-inverses">biinvertible maps are quasi-invertible</link> and <link href="erct-002M.xml" type="local" addr="erct-002M" title="Quasi-invertible maps are contractible">quasi-invertible maps are contractible</link>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree></backlinks> <references/></backmatter></tree>